rows.label: qst200403_msg0001
rows.name:
Loan shark? Dunno...
Never heard of 'em.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0002
rows.name:
But there are some other guys
you should watch out for.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0003
rows.name:
Lately, there are people in
this city who'll intentionally
get hurt to extort you.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0004
rows.name:
What's worse though is that there's a
doctor working with them, "charging"
the "injured" stupidly high fees.

rows.label: qst200403_msg0005
rows.name:
You all be careful not to get
caught by those scumbags.
